OL,4,G1855FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe week's final visit is to Marc
OL,6,     Gand Matt's gastropub in Kent. The
OL,7,     Gpair have been building
OL,8,     Gexpectations throughout the week
OL,9,     G- will their place live up to the
OL,10,     Ghype?
OL,11,G1925FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GWill one guest's pernickety
OL,13,     Gprotests about a path prove
OL,14,     Gpivotal in providing a plaque-
OL,15,     Gwinner on payment day? It's all
OL,16,     Gkicking off!
