OL,4,G2000F24 Hours in A&E
OL,5,     GThis episode explores the
OL,6,     Gimportance of family. Mike, who's
OL,7,     G79, has collapsed in the street.
OL,8,     GChartered surveyor Andrew has
OL,9,     Gtripped on a paving slab and has
OL,10,     Ga suspected dislocated shoulder.
OL,11,G2100F24 Hours in A&E
OL,12,     GKing's College Hospital in London
OL,13,     Ghas one of Britain's busiest A&E
OL,14,     Gdepartments. In this episode, two
OL,15,     Gcyclists arrive in A&E, and a
OL,16,     Gretired docker takes a shine to
OL,17,     Gnurse Laura.
